gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tzuOT5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tzuOT5.png&h=a89d897c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舖名：茶痴<br />\n地址：上環文咸東街14號<br />\n<br />\n點解佢係黃？ 佢哋係重要日子都會唔開門，做正確的事！連佢個公仔都要戴埋口罩啊，戴住口罩點飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBefore<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxAxMHx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxAxMHx.png&h=421a2987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAfter <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w16QynB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw16QynB.png&h=ca0f311d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有學生優惠，老細寄語：年輕人係社會棟樑，千萬要萬事小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndDb2ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndDb2ff.png&h=cf0976c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舖頭成日都有新品推出，私心推介芝士茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cAHgtWe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAHgtWe.jpg&h=fb03b333&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TYzfBf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TYzfBf.png&h=63d6c6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳送門<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/chichahongkong?igshid=13cg86rx7iy0j\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fchichahongkong%3Figshid%3D13cg86rx7iy0j&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=53d0cc27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/chichahongkong?igshid=13cg86rx7iy0j</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/chichahongkong/?ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fchichahongkong%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal%26mt_nav%3D0&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=f8f4f3d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/chichahongkong/?ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好再飲喜茶啦，香港其實有好多選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣就幫襯下啦，人哋都罷工咗好多日<br />\n我愛黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T11:24:22.000Z","msg":"冇得坐架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239804915814f7d4514f4e6068cf0ddada35a234","tid":1773031,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"皇茶個芝士奶蓋都幾好飲"},{"pid":"881984019a5481c8a3aa5236dec16e496e25d525","tid":1773031,"uid":13143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T11:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1760289ceefa0ce14dbeb8499b9c020be1446db5","tid":1773031,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab61d74196029a9d2ad9cbe866d2e1b35c305bad","tid":1773031,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"239804915814f7d4514f4e6068cf0ddada35a234","tid":1773031,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"皇茶個芝士奶蓋都幾好飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T11:35:08.000Z","msg":"講緊旺角個間"},{"pid":"a508c786192c4c2a943ff68c1bfa37bbd3802c84","tid":1773031,"uid":16706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cfe6f708aa97008eef62d62e545f53b359c65a36","tid":1773031,"